To Install and run the restaurant listing and review app, you will need to follow these steps:

1. Make sure you have Node.js installed if not visit official Node.js website (https://nodejs.org) and install the latest version for you operating system.

2. Fork the repository in your local system.

3. After Forking, open terminal and run npm install in the project directory.
   this will install all the necessary dependencies for running the app.

4. Configure the database with your own collection, username and password of mysql workbench database.

5. after database configuration start the server from terminal using command 'npm start'.

6. now your server will be up on port 3000 now u just have to insert restaurants in the database, restaurants table. then open the Homepage.html file in your browser.

Now the restaurant listing and review app is fully functionable.
